parameters.AUDIO_REVERB_DRY_LEVEL: 0: The level of the dry signal (dB). The value is between -20 and 10.

parameters.AUDIO_REVERB_WET_LEVEL: 1: The level of the early reflection signal (wet signal) (dB). The value is between -20 and 10.

parameters.AUDIO_REVERB_ROOM_SIZE: 2: The room size of the reflection. The value is between 0 and 100.

parameters.AUDIO_REVERB_WET_DELAY: 3: The length of the initial delay of the wet signal (ms). The value is between 0 and 200.

parameters.AUDIO_REVERB_STRENGTH: 4: The reverberation strength. The value is between 0 and 100.
